
#hashtag for message

Create Repository :  
                git init  #(create local repository)

Syncing Repository : 
                git remote add origin "C:\Users\Jagmohan Singh\Documents\Git"
                git pull origin master       #get all the files from central repository                 
                
                
 Making changes :
 
                git status   #files which are in index  and which we can add to index so that we can commit change in local repository
                git add myfile.txt   #file are added in index
                git commit -m "we can write our message here..like adding 1st commit in local repository"
                
                git add -A   	#add all the files in index 
                git commit -a  #commit all the files
                
                git log   #see all 
